(31400, 'Sprialypsy 500 mg 30 oral disintegrating tabs.', 'سبيراليبسي 500مجم 30 قرص ذائب بالفم', '84', '138', 'Levetiracetam', 'Mash premiere > sas pharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مضاد للصرع', 'Anti-epileptic.pyrrolidine', '500 mg', 'Levetiracetam is indicated as an adjunctive therapy in the treatment of partial onset seizures in epileptic patients who are one month of age and older. Additionally, it is indicated as an adjunct in the treatment of myoclonic seizures in patients with juvenile myoclonic epilepsy who are 12 years of age and older, and in primary generalized tonic-clonic seizures in patients with idiopathic generalized epilepsy who are 6 years of age and older.[L8606]
